note: My boss once described me as a Renaissance man. It was an incredible complement for someone with too many interests and too little time. amateur radio general license (KC9UNZ), GMRS (WRYP955), open source software enthusiast, Web site developer for a number of not for profits. 30+ years supporting technology with an M.Div and 20 years in the parish (yes they overlapped). Oh and I play woodwinds and sing tenor as well.
